2025-09-05FINFinancial Administration ActAppointment to the Canada Deposit Insurance CorporationAppointment of Gina Byrne of Ottawa, Ontario, to be President and Chief Executive Officer of the Canada Deposit Insurance Corporation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of eighteen months, or until such a time as a new President and Chief Executive Officer is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective October 1, 2025.N/A
subject: Appointment to the Canada Deposit Insurance Corporation
precis: Appointment of Gina Byrne of Ottawa, Ontario, to be President and Chief Executive Officer of the Canada Deposit Insurance Corporation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of eighteen months, or until such a time as a new President and Chief Executive Officer is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective October 1, 2025.
